  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 157\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "157 lakhs of gold will not be released from a katun",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An employee of the duty-free shopping complex was arrested last night after trying to take 60 gold biscuits weighing 0.6 kg and 995 grams worth Rs. He is a 35-year-old resident of Ja-Ala area.",
        "He prepared these gold biscuits into 06 parcels of ten each, hid them in his waist area and was taking them out of the airport when he was arrested by a group of Katunayake airport security officers.",
        "Later, this person and the stock of gold biscuits he was carrying have been handed over to the airport customs officials for further investigation.",
        "The customs officials suspect that these gold biscuits were brought from Dubai to Katunayake airport, and it has been revealed in the preliminary investigations carried out by the customs that he had arranged for this stock of gold biscuits to be taken out of the airport.",
        "Appraisers have confirmed to customs that all these gold biscuits are 24 carat single pound gold. The Katunayake airport customs officers have also detained this trade employee and are conducting further investigations on this matter."
      ],
